headline.print_headline: Spain Soccer Team Starts Fund for Evicted Woman
headline.main: Spain Soccer Team Starts Fund for Evicted Woman

lead_paragraph: A Spanish soccer team opened a bank account Thursday to collect donations for an 85-year-old woman whose eviction last week from her Madrid apartment sparked an outcry, team officials said.
